		<!-- message -->
		<div>Anyone else think that it was an extremely stupid idea to give the Bazaar such a complicated layout? Two dozen separate small rooms connected by small tunnels and teleporters?<br />
<br />
What's the point in this? Reducing lag? That's what Hide All Traders is for, on lower end systems. Making more room for traders? No need for such an elaborate zone design to accomplish that. Adding the zone line to the Barter zone? A stupid, oversized portal worked for PoK.<br />
<br />
Good job on actually making it harder to find traders when it was perfectly fine before!</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
